data.description: Welcome to your home in the serene Anchor Haven II subdivision of Pleasant Hope! This spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence is a haven of comfort and style. From the moment you step through the door, you're greeted by the airy ambiance of the split-level entryway and the abundance of natural light streaming through the many windows in the living room, enhanced by the soaring high ceilings. Designed with both functionality and aesthetics in mind, this home boasts a thoughtful layout that seamlessly blends practicality with elegance. The generously-sized living room provides the perfect setting for gatherings and relaxation, offering a picturesque view of the surrounding landscape through its numerous windows.'The heart of the home, the kitchen, features modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar for casual dining. Adjacent to the kitchen is the dining area, ideal for hosting intimate dinners or larger gatherings.Outside, the large fenced-in backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor recreation and entertainment, whether it's gardening, playtime with pets, or simply enjoying the fresh air in privacy. The oversized garage provides ample storage space for vehicles, tools, and outdoor gear, ensuring that everything has its place.  Schedule a showing today
